{
  "texts": [
    "However, it misclassified all true variants as artifacts.",
    "We considered the variant calls detected in the FFPE-only samples as FFPE-artifacts.",
    "However, we cannot rule out the possibility that some of the FFPE-only artifacts are true subclonal variants not detected in the matched FF sample due to regional genetic heterogeneity.",
    "Thus, we used FF and FFPE samples with the same genetic make-up.",
    "Additionally, we wanted to evaluate DEEPOMICS FFPE on a new dataset."
  ]
}